{"id":"eae56ed9-3f44-44d0-b83a-9ca3ba9ad803","title":"1509/06","type":"main-list-block","children":[{"id":"7a1c5aed-6a86-4a52-aa5a-67ec8d72ae1d","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"From Rome, June, 1509.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"fd1c1752-1dac-479a-908e-c4b8530ac579","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":5,"end":8,"value":"501a8a32-2c8a-4934-9060-8c7e36339f0f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"7769cad6-04ea-4116-8697-7e8c73693fd8","type":"codex/time-reference","start":11,"end":20,"value":"619888ff-6012-4427-8d23-5d554fdbcc7f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"e28463e6-8021-4608-a6b3-95fa935a637e","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"To Lodovico di Buonarrota Simoni,","standoffProperties":[{"id":"c847dba2-9009-4ebc-a448-f0c1bdfa1a82","type":"style/italics","start":0,"end":31,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"9265ad59-b725-40e8-a24d-9acfd5086b8b","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":31,"value":"21671569-3eea-412b-85cc-08f659f58019","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"b9628efd-a95b-401b-87c0-539eb3e0b03d","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"in Florence.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"190c08b2-9168-48ef-a535-785caecd3b4d","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":10,"value":"671ee7e7-ae1b-4a5a-9591-b40203d5108f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"af4e4813-d960-4116-a5cf-cd86e86cb757","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"Most Revered Father,\u00A0\u2014\u00A0Some days ago I sent you a hundred broad ducats of the money I was keeping here for my expenses of living and working, and this I did because I think the money is safer in\u00A0Florence, than here. I expect you have received it.\u00A0I beg you to take it to the Spedalingo and tell him to place it to my account with the other money. I have now eighty ducats left here, which I think will maintain me for four months, and I have still six months work to do before I shall receive any money from the Pope. Of a surety, therefore, I shall be in\u00A0want of money, and I think I shall require another\u00A0fifty ducats. I beg, therefore, that of the hundred\u00A0ducats you have promised to pay back to me, you will let me have have fifty: the remainder I give to you on condition that within four months the money is\u00A0ready without fail, because I shall have need of it here, I want to save the hundred I am sending to Florence in order to pay them to the heirs of the\u00A0Cardinal of Siena, for otherwise, as you know, this sum must be withdrawn from my funds in Santa Maria Nuova. I beg of you to buy a farm without\u00A0fail, because I hear that they are to be had cheap. When my painting here is finished I shall be entitled\u00A0to receive a thousand ducats from the Pope, and if\u00A0it turns out well I hope to be paid without fail. Pray to God therefore for the Pope and for us.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"fe370a23-aa60-43d4-b24a-f6e246e25f46","type":"style/uppercase","start":0,"end":18,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"b89f2506-4be0-43d5-b5f9-60f9c94416b2","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":18,"value":"21671569-3eea-412b-85cc-08f659f58019","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"f3544f4e-c723-428b-9e01-73d917a3d13d","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":37,"end":37,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"f49dae97-e24b-449a-ae6c-bdc18f3125d5","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":44,"end":46,"value":"21671569-3eea-412b-85cc-08f659f58019","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"79a87452-1a94-4fd9-bdef-8a40d345d4c2","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":84,"end":84,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"b2d75c30-2e39-444c-8e4b-d3da88ccb38c","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":107,"end":108,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"057fd87d-9fdd-481b-b8f1-904e441f9c78","ty